'''Ringwinner''' was one of the names that [[Bilbo Baggins]] used for himself when the dragon [[Smaug]] asked him who he was, because he wanted to know his usual name.<ref>{{H|Inside}}</ref> Bilbo had found [[the One Ring]] on the floor of a tunnel in an [[Orcs|orc]]-hold of the [[Misty Mountains]] before his encounter with Smaug.<ref>{{H|Riddles}}</ref>
